# Hybrid Licensing Policy: E3 Framework

The E3 Framework (Effective, Efficient, Elegant) uses a dual-license model to protect academic integrity while promoting community innovation.

## 1. Code & Software (Apache License 2.0)
The following directories and their contents are licensed under the **Apache License 2.0**:
- e3-evaluator/
- examples/
- scripts/ (if any)

## 2. Documentation & Research (CC BY 4.0)
The following directories and their contents are licensed under the **Creative Commons Attribution 4.0 International (CC BY 4.0)**:
- framework/
- paper/
- figures/
- tables/

